Cyborg Slunks is an album by Buckethead, released on October 30, 2007. It is currently available only through TDRS Music.[1]
The music features Buckethead accompanied by the Cyborg Slunk Percussion Ensemble conducted by Albert.

The album will first be released as a limited-edition version with each cover numbered and hand drawn by Buckethead. A non-limited edition will be made available at a later date.

The accompanying pictures show two different covers of the limited-edition album.
